      </div>
    </button>
    <h2
      class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-[64px] lg:text-[80px] font-medium bg-gradient-to-r text-white leading-tight"
    >
      The <strong class="text-blue">BIGGEST DevFest</strong> event in&nbsp;Indonesia
      is coming
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl md:2xl lg:text-3xl text-white mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Catch up on the latest from Tech Conferences, Workshops, Panel Discussion, <br
        class="hidden lg:inline"
      /> Women Empowerment, and Live Podcasts. Don't miss out!
    </p>
    <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-32">
      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <time class="font-bold text-2xl">Sat, 29 November 2025</time>
        <address class="text-xs not-italic text-start">
          Universitas Kristen Maranatha, Bandung
        </address>
      </div>
      <a
        href="https://goers.co/devfestbdg25"
        target="_blank"
        class="bg-blue hover:bg-dark-blue border-2 border-dark-blue font-medium text-white text-xl px-8 py-6 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer justify-center"
      >
